    "description": "AP Kindred build with Liandry's Anguish. You and Wolf watching the world burn together. With DOTs.",
    "how to play": [
      "AP Kindred build is focused on W. Your goal with this build is to annoy your enemy by spamming W to poke.",
      "Your W is going to be bread and butter of this build. It works with Arcane Comet, <b>Liandry's Anguish</b>, <b>Demonic Embrace</b> and Rylai's Crystal Scepter. And it scales with AP too.",
      "You can cast W and move to be at the very edge of it, so you are outside enemy poke.",
      "You can offset low AP scaling of your build by buying <b>Lich Bane</b> and <b>Nashor's Tooth</b> and do some auto attacking.",
      "This build is very off-meta and not performing good in every scenario, but it is fun to play."
